article_id:438,category_name:News,title_name:Epilogue Added to the Fire Emblem: Lost Heroes Event,image_path:,message:<div>An epilogue has been added to the Fire Emblem: Lost Heroes event, which ended <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1557813599"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>You can view the epilogue by tapping the banner on the upper-left corner of the Home screen, which can be accessed from the in-game footer menu, then selecting View Quests within Special Events.</div><div><br></div><div>â– Epilogue Availability</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1557813600"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1558418399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Note:</div><div>The epilogue can be viewed only by players who have completed up to chapter 7 of the event&rsquo;s story.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1557813600,update_time1556271474